template(name="pro")
  .pro
    .row-fluid
      .container-fluid
        .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2.col-xs-12
          .jumbotron
            h1 Support a PRO
            p Support an indie designer to build the Monospace PRO platform
            ul.pager
              li
                a() Become a founding member for 24$ per year

    .row
      .container
          .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-0.col-md-4.col-md-offset-0
            h1
              span.fa.fa-terminal            
            h5 Own Domain & Branding
            p Remove all references to the Monospace Platform, show your own logo and use your own custom domain name - but keep all the power of the platform.
          .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-0.col-md-4.col-md-offset-0
            h1
              span.fa.fa-code
            h5 Themes
            p Trends come and go. Stay on top of trends, and technical practices, by selecting from a variety of professionally built themes. With just one click.
          .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-0.col-md-4.col-md-offset-0
            h1
              span.fa.fa-area-chart            
            h5 Analytics
            p How would you like me to chop up your Dribbble data to show you how well your shots work, how well your profile is being received, or how much interest is being shown by Talent Scouts and head hunters?


    .row
      .container
        .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-0.col-md-4.col-md-offset-0
          h5 Scout? Find Talent
          p Monospace PRO for Talent Scouts offers insights into the best Dribbble talent.
        
        .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-0.col-md-4.col-md-offset-0
          +subscribe
